definition: Yushu county level city in Changchun 長春|长春, Jilin
Yushu county level city in Changchun 長春|长春, Jilin

sentences.chinese: 榆樹大街橡樹大街交界處聚衆鬥毆。

sentences.english: High Street separates here into East Street and Elm Street.
sentences.chinese: 高街在此分爲東街和榆樹街。

sentences.english: Ulmus pumila open forest ecosystem plays an important role in Otindag Sandy Land.
sentences.chinese: 榆樹疏林生態系統是渾善達克沙地的重要組分之一。

sentences.english: The elm trees before Court Leys were beginning to burst into leaf.
sentences.chinese: 萊伊府第房子前面的榆樹開始長出嫩葉。

sentences.english: We walked down a stately avenue of elms.
sentences.chinese: 我們沿着兩旁有榆樹的大街步行。

sentences.english: The disease blighted oaks and elms.
sentences.chinese: 疾病使櫟樹和榆樹枯萎。

sentences.english: Beneath those rugged elms, that yew-tree's shade.
sentences.chinese: 那些粗糙的老榆樹下，紫杉蔭裏。

sentences.english: Autumn is riding on the old elm tree after the teaching building of the yellow leaves fly it?
sentences.chinese: 秋天是乘着教學樓後那棵老榆樹的黃葉飛走的嗎？

sentences.english: That implied elm trees may play an important role on the accretion and fixation of sand dunes.
sentences.chinese: 這表明榆樹對當地沙丘的形成和固定起主要作用。

sentences.english: The moan of doves in immemorial elms.
sentences.chinese: 古老的榆樹林中鴿子的呢喃。

sentences.english: I want to report a fire on 12 Elm Road.
sentences.chinese: 我想要報火警，榆樹路12號失火了。

sentences.english: The forest of the Far West supplied the best oaks and elms.
sentences.chinese: 遠西森林裏有很好的橡樹和榆樹。

sentences.english: The old lane that used to connect Elm Street to riverbanks was overgrown.
sentences.chinese: 從前連接榆樹街和河岸的那條小道已經長滿了草木。

sentences.english: Sleeping in the elm may be invigorating, but it is also illegal.
sentences.chinese: 睡在榆樹上可能很爽，卻是違法的。

sentences.english: Each living district in the city is round with elms.
sentences.chinese: 城內每個生活區的四周都用榆樹修成籬笆。
